thread.title_full: Matboard and More reviewed by Customer123456

author: Customer123456
title: Customer123456
text: Using Matboard and More to buy customized mats for two picture frames was easy, and I could not be happier with the finished product. I have two frames with odd dimensions, and I could not find mats anywhere, and I hated the look of my pictures in the frames without a mat. Matboard and More is easy to use online, the colors I got were great, and it was delivered within a week. Excellent quality, excellent product.
